# Physics Teaching Simulator - Planning Document

## Project Vision
Interactive 2D retro-style physics simulator for teaching mechanics and fluid mechanics.
Focus: "Known functions" (pre-built scenarios) with parameter tweaking, real-time visualization, and educational overlays.

## Tech Stack
- **Core**: Pygame (retro 2D interactive)
- **Physics**: NumPy + SciPy + custom solvers (optionally Pymunk)
- **Math**: SymPy for equations
- **UI**: Custom retro-style menus and sliders
- **Assets**: Pixel art

